<h2>Welcome <%= @user.first_name %>!</h2>

<p>Thank you for signing up for The Art Exchange! We're excited to have you join our community of concert poster collectors and music enthusiasts.</p>

<p>To get started, please confirm your email address by clicking the button below:</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
  <a href="<%= @confirmation_url %>" class="btn-primary" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #c10230; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">
    Confirm Email Address
  </a>
</div>

<p>Once confirmed, you'll be able to:</p>
<ul style="margin: 16px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
  <li>Browse and discover concert posters from your favorite artists</li>
  <li>Create your personal collection</li>
  <li>Get notified about new additions</li>
  <li>Connect with other collectors</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>This confirmation link will expire in 24 hours.</strong></p>

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #a7a9ac; border: 1px solid #f3f4f6; padding: 16px; border-radius: 6px; background-color: #fafaf9;">
  <strong>Can't click the button?</strong> Copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
  <span style="word-break: break-all;"><%= @confirmation_url %></span>
</p>